title: US races to huge lead at gymnastics worlds in Scotland
text:
> Top News US races to huge lead at gymnastics worlds in Scotland China's Yilin Fan performs during her beam routine as she takes part in the women's qualification competition at the World Artistic Gymnastics championships in Glasgow, Scotland, Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015.
